MPlayer
=======

Enable Pulse Audio support in MPlayer.

     $ cat <<EOF
     let
       pkgs = (import <nixpkgs>) {};
     in
       pkgs.MPlayer.override { pulseSupport = true; }
     EOF > ~/.nix-defexpr/mplayer.nix

Install MPlayer with Pulse Audio support.

     $ nix-env -iA mplayer

Make Pulse Audio the default output device.

     $ cat <<EOF
     ao=pulse
     >> ~/.mplayer/config
